{
  "stem": "5740.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We worked together, every piece of bread we shared together, every piece of-- if we had any-- a shoe or anything, a, a frock we shared together.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She is in, in a, in Israel, and I'm-- in a kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And each time I'm in Israel, I visit her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when I was last time there with my daughter, she said, did you tell your daughter what happened to, to us-- how you behaved?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I say, I've never tell anything because I, I couldn't talk.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "For many years, I didn't say a thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't tell you even-- anyhow, she, she couldn't speak English.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my daughter couldn't understand English.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My daughter couldn't understand Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she didn't speak English.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she told my daughter, you know what your mother done?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We used to have-- we used to work at the same machines, one next to another, and somebody was bringing us the merchandise that we were supposed to put on the, on the machine.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was a Frenchman.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the Frenchmen sometimes brought-- outside there, there were, there were prisoners of war of South African Englishmen.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we know we could eye them or something like this and sometimes they, they, they-- the Englishmen brought us-- the Frenchmen brought us a letter from one of those boyfriends of us.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "South African.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were-- we got this letter, and we started to read it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the [NON-ENGLISH] called us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What was the [NON-ENGLISH]?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The [NON-ENGLISH] was the one who overlooked this particular hole where we were working.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How did you say?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A foreman.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "More than a foreman, a meister.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he was in charge of that whole--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In charge, in charge of this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he called it.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
